snippet.title: Rosa Gamazo
snippet.description:
I am a journalist from Madrid, Spain, based in Los Angeles. I interview actors and directors for their movie releases under a different angle. If you like Emilia Clarke, Keanu Reeves, Jason Momoa, Ben Affleck, Ryan Reynolds, Jeff Bridges, Blake Lively or any other big movie star check out my channel.
Thanks for watching my channel.
